   Search Title 17 Regulations

      The text, titles, definitions, authority and references of Title 17 of
      the California Code of Regulations can be searched using simple and
      advanced word searches and Boolean logic.

   Locate Information Using Eureka:

      Eureka Search Engine Eureka is a WWW search site for all State of
      California public Web pages.

      To focus your search on the Department of Developmental Services' Web
      pages, include URL:DDS in your search criteria. For example, to search
      for pages on the DDS Web site that provides information about autism,
      you could enter the following as your search criteria:
      URL:DDS AND "autism"

      If the information you are seeking cannot be found with Eureka, we
      recommend you try one of the following Internet search sites:
        * AltaVista
        * Excite
        * HotBot
        * InfoSeek
        * Lycos
        * Yahoo
